m sequences do not lead to a major dust storm. Zonal wavenumber analysis of\neddy kinetic energy shows that the peaks of the $1<P\\leq8$ eddies often result\nfrom combinations of zonal wavenumbers 1 to 3, while the $P\\leq1$ eddies and\n$8<P\\leq60$ sol eddies are each dominated by zonal wavenumber 1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 19:14:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-04"}
