tes that this gradient approach offers a transparent\nunderstanding of the contributions controlling the slope of the curvature\nspectrum. As an application of our findings, we characterise the slope in\nfrequency of a stochastic gravitational wave background generated at second\norder from curvature fluctuations, using the more accurate information we\ngained on the shape of curvature power spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 19:48:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2019 19:23:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2020 18:23:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-06"}
