d the ones from semi-classical expansion, which shows\ncoincidence for weak electromagnetic fields and small spin imbalance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2019 02:56:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-04"}
