 most\nimportant physical ingredient to be settled for a quantitative prediction of\nthe inner crust properties is the surface tension at extreme isospin values.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2019 09:51:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-11"}
